  "SA07n941:192": "sukhaṃ svapiti vāste vā yatra tatra gatoddhavaḥ ||38 ||",
  "SA07n941:193": "teṣāṃ hi satataṃ loke viṣayānabhikāṅkṣatām |",
  "SA07n941:194": "saṃvinnaivāsti kārpaṇyācchunāmāśāvatāmiva ||39 ||",
  "SA07n941:195": "viṣayairindriyagrāmo na tṛptimadhigacchati |",
  "SA07n941:196": "ajasraṃ pūryamāṇo'pi samudraḥ salilairiva ||40 ||",
  "SA07n941:197": "avaśyaṃ gocare sve sve vartitavyamihendriyaiḥ |",
  "SA07n941:198": "nimittaṃ tatra na grāhyamanuvyañjanameva ca ||41 ||",
  "SA07n941:199": "ālokya cakṣuṣā rūpaṃ dhātumātre vyavasthitaḥ |",
  "SA07n941:200": "strī veti puruṣo veti na kalpayitumarhasi ||42 ||",
  "SA07n941:201": "sacet strīpuruṣagrāhaḥ kvacid vidyeta kaścan |",
  "SA07n941:202": "śubhataḥ keśadantādīnnānuprasthātumarhasi ||43 ||",
  "SA07n941:203": "nāpaneyaṃ tataḥ kiṃcit prakṣepyaṃ nāpi kiñcana |",
  "SA07n941:204": "draṣṭavyaṃ bhūtato bhūtaṃ yādṛśaṃ ca yathā ca yat ||44 ||",
  "SA07n941:205": "evaṃ te paśyatastattvaṃ śaśvadindriyagocaram |",
  "SA07n941:206": "bhaviṣyati padasthānaṃ nābhidhyādaurmanasyayoḥ ||45 ||",
  "SA07n941:207": "abhidhyā priyarūpeṇa hanti kāmātmakaṃ jagat |",
  "SA07n941:208": "arirmitramukheneva priyavākkaluṣāśayaḥ ||46 ||",
  "SA07n941:209": "daurmanasyābhidhānastu pratigho viṣayāśritaḥ |",
  "SA07n941:210": "mohādyenānuvṛtena paratreha ca hanyate ||47 ||",
  "SA07n941:211": "anurodhavirodhābhyāṃ śitoṣṇābhyāmivārditaḥ |",
  "SA07n941:212": "śarma nāpnoti na śreyaścalendriyamato jagat ||48 ||",
  "SA07n941:213": "nendriyaṃ viṣaye tāvat pravṛttamapi sajjate |",
  "SA07n941:214": "yāvanna manasastatra parikalpaḥ pravartate ||49 ||",
  "SA07n941:215": "indhane sati vāyau ca yathā jvalati pāvakaḥ |",
  "SA07n941:216": "viṣayāt parikalpācca kleśāgnirjāyate tathā ||50 ||",
  "SA07n941:217": "abhūtaparikalpena viṣayasya hi vadhyate |",
  "SA07n941:218": "tameva viṣayaṃ paśyan bhūtataḥ parimucyate ||51 ||",
  "SA07n941:219": "dṛṣṭvaikaṃ rūpamanyo hi rajyate'nyaḥ praduṣyati |",
  "SA07n941:220": "kaścid bhavati madhyasthastatraivānyo ghṛṇāyate ||52 ||",
  "SA07n941:221": "ato na viṣayo heturbandhāya na vimuktaye |",
  "SA07n941:222": "parikalpaviśeṣeṇa saṃgo bhavati vā na vā ||53 ||",
  "SA07n941:223": "kāryaḥ paramayatnena tasmādindriyasaṃvaraḥ |",
  "SA07n941:224": "indriyāṇi hyagutpāni duḥkhāya ca bhavāya ca ||54 ||",
  "SA07n941:225": "kāmabhogabhogavadbhirātmadṛṣṭidṛṣṭibhiḥ pramādanaikamūrddhabhiḥ praharṣalolajivhakaiḥ |",
  "SA07n941:226": "indriyoragairmanobilaśrayaiḥ spṛhāviṣaiḥ śamāgadādṛte na dṛṣṭamasti yaccikitset ||55 ||",
  "SA07n941:227": "tasmādeṣāmakuśalakarāṇāmarīṇāṃ cakṣurghrāṇaśravaṇarasanasparśanānām |",
  "SA07n941:228": "sarvāvasthaṃ bhava viniyamādapramatto māsminnarthe kṣaṇamapi kṛthāstvaṃ pramādam ||56 ||",
  "SA07n941:229": "saundarananda mahākāvye “śīla evaṃ indriya-saṃyama“ nāma trayodaśa sarga samāpta |"
}